### ğŸ”¹ 2ï¸âƒ£ So Why Does Your Code Still Give Correct Output?

Because â€” youâ€™re **not using the mapâ€™s order** at all when checking for the first non-repeating character.
Instead, youâ€™re **iterating over the original string** again ğŸ‘‡

```java
