âœ… This loop ensures youâ€™re checking characters in the **same order as they appeared in the string**.

Youâ€™re *only* using the map to **store counts**, not to decide order.
So even if the map stores `{a=3, c=1, b=2, d=1, e=1}` internally in random order,
