## ğŸ—£ï¸ Interview-Ready Answer

> â€œBy default, `HashMap` doesnâ€™t maintain insertion order â€” it arranges entries based on hash codes.
> However, in this problem, order doesnâ€™t matter during counting, because we again iterate over the string to find the first non-repeating character in the original order.
